[
  {
    "id": "238697ed-76ee-44ef-8020-d394cebb3a55",
    "context": "templates",
    "data": {
      "name": "propuesta_comercial",
      "html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html lang=\"es\">\r\n\r\n<head>\r\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\r\n  <title>{{pdfTitle}}</title>\r\n  <link\r\n    href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Alegreya+Sans:wght@400;700;800;900&family=Inter:wght@400;600;700;900&display=swap\"\r\n    rel=\"stylesheet\">\r\n  <style>\r\n    * {\r\n      box-sizing: border-box;\r\n      margin: 0;\r\n      padding: 0;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    body {\r\n      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;\r\n      background-color: #FFFFFF;\r\n      color: #2D2D2D;\r\n      line-height: 1.6;\r\n      padding: 40px;\r\n      -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .quote-container {\r\n      max-width: 900px;\r\n      margin: 0 auto;\r\n      border: 1px solid #EAEAEA;\r\n      padding: 50px;\r\n      background: #FFFFFF;\r\n      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.02);\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    /* Luxury Header */\r\n    .brand-section {\r\n      display: flex;\r\n      justify-content: space-between;\r\n      align-items: flex-start;\r\n      border-bottom: 2px solid #C5A059;\r\n      padding-bottom: 25px;\r\n      margin-bottom: 40px;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .brand-logo h1 {\r\n      font-family: 'Alegreya Sans', sans-serif;\r\n      font-size: 32px;\r\n      font-weight: 900;\r\n      font-weight: 700;\r\n      letter-spacing: 0.15em;\r\n      color: #1A1A1A;\r\n      text-transform: uppercase;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .brand-logo p.brand-subtitle {\r\n      font-size: 10px;\r\n      font-weight: 700;\r\n      text-transform: uppercase;\r\n      letter-spacing: 0.3em;\r\n      color: #C5A059;\r\n      margin-top: 4px;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .brand-logo p.brand-contact {\r\n      font-size: 9.5px;\r\n      font-weight: 600;\r\n      color: #777777;\r\n      margin-top: 8px;\r\n      letter-spacing: 0.05em;\r\n      text-transform: none;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .proposal-meta {\r\n      text-align: right;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .proposal-meta h2 {\r\n      font-family: 'Alegreya Sans', sans-serif;\r\n      font-weight: 800;\r\n      font-size: 18px;\r\n      font-weight: 600;\r\n      letter-spacing: 0.05em;\r\n      color: #1A1A1A;\r\n      margin-bottom: 6px;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .proposal-meta p {\r\n      font-size: 11px;\r\n      font-weight: 600;\r\n      text-transform: uppercase;\r\n      color: #777777;\r\n      letter-spacing: 0.1em;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    /* Client info card */\r\n    .info-grid {\r\n      display: grid;\r\n      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\r\n      gap: 30px;\r\n      margin-bottom: 40px;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .info-block h4 {\r\n      font-size: 10px;\r\n      font-weight: 900;\r\n      text-transform: uppercase;\r\n      letter-spacing: 0.15em;\r\n      color: #C5A059;\r\n      margin-bottom: 10px;\r\n      border-bottom: 1px solid #F1ECE1;\r\n      padding-bottom: 4px;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .info-block p {\r\n      font-size: 12px;\r\n      color: #4D4D4D;\r\n      margin-bottom: 4px;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .info-block strong {\r\n      color: #1A1A1A;\r\n      font-weight: 700;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .info-block.full-width {\r\n      grid-column: span 2;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    /* Section divider & Titles */\r\n    .section-title {\r\n      font-family: 'Alegreya Sans', sans-serif;\r\n      font-size: 16px;\r\n      font-weight: 800;\r\n      text-transform: uppercase;\r\n      letter-spacing: 0.12em;\r\n      color: #1A1A1A;\r\n      margin-bottom: 20px;\r\n      border-left: 3.5px solid #C5A059;\r\n      padding-left: 12px;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    /* Executive summary */\r\n    .options-container {\r\n      display: grid;\r\n      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));\r\n      gap: 20px;\r\n      margin-bottom: 45px;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .option-card {\r\n      border: 1px solid #E5E5E5;\r\n      border-radius: 6px;\r\n      padding: 20px;\r\n      background: #FAFAFA;\r\n      transition: all 0.3s ease;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .option-card.selected {\r\n      border-color: #C5A059;\r\n      background: #FCFAF6;\r\n      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(197, 160, 89, 0.08);\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .option-header {\r\n      display: flex;\r\n      justify-content: space-between;\r\n      align-items: center;\r\n      margin-bottom: 12px;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .option-title {\r\n      font-size: 10px;\r\n      font-weight: 900;\r\n      letter-spacing: 0.1em;\r\n      color: #666666;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .option-card.selected .option-title {\r\n      color: #C5A059;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .selected-badge {\r\n      font-size: 8px;\r\n      font-weight: 900;\r\n      color: #FFFFFF;\r\n      background: #C5A059;\r\n      padding: 2px 6px;\r\n      border-radius: 20px;\r\n      letter-spacing: 0.05em;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .option-price {\r\n      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;\r\n      font-size: 20px;\r\n      font-weight: 700;\r\n      color: #1A1A1A;\r\n      margin-bottom: 6px;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .option-diff {\r\n      font-size: 10px;\r\n      color: #777777;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    /* Space section details */\r\n    .space-section {\r\n      border: 1px solid #EAEAEA;\r\n      border-radius: 8px;\r\n      padding: 20px;\r\n      margin-bottom: 25px;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .space-title {\r\n      font-family: 'Alegreya Sans', sans-serif;\r\n      font-weight: 800;\r\n      font-size: 15px;\r\n      font-weight: 700;\r\n      text-transform: uppercase;\r\n      letter-spacing: 0.1em;\r\n      color: #1A1A1A;\r\n      margin-bottom: 15px;\r\n      border-bottom: 1px solid #EAEAEA;\r\n      padding-bottom: 8px;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    /* Table styling */\r\n    .items-table {\r\n      width: 100%;\r\n      border-collapse: collapse;\r\n      margin-bottom: 15px;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .items-table th {\r\n      background: #FAFAFA;\r\n      font-size: 9px;\r\n      font-weight: 800;\r\n      text-transform: uppercase;\r\n      letter-spacing: 0.08em;\r\n      color: #6B7280;\r\n      padding: 8px 12px;\r\n      text-align: left;\r\n      border-bottom: 1px solid #E5E7EB;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .items-table td {\r\n      padding: 8px 12px;\r\n      font-size: 11px;\r\n      color: #374151;\r\n      border-bottom: 1px solid #F3F4F6;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .items-table tr:last-child td {\r\n      border-bottom: none;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .items-table .center {\r\n      text-align: center;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .items-table .right {\r\n      text-align: right;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .empty-row {\r\n      text-align: center !important;\r\n      color: #999999 !important;\r\n      font-style: italic;\r\n      padding: 20px !important;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    /* Labor collapsed bar */\r\n    .labor-bar-collapsed {\r\n      background: #FCFAF6;\r\n      border: 1px dashed #E5DEC9;\r\n      border-radius: 6px;\r\n      padding: 10px 15px;\r\n      display: flex;\r\n      justify-content: space-between;\r\n      align-items: center;\r\n      margin-bottom: 20px;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .labor-summary-title {\r\n      font-size: 10px;\r\n      font-weight: 900;\r\n      text-transform: uppercase;\r\n      letter-spacing: 0.1em;\r\n      color: #C5A059;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .labor-summary-days {\r\n      font-size: 11px;\r\n      font-weight: 700;\r\n      color: #5E533F;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    /* Space sub-totals block */\r\n    .space-totals {\r\n      display: flex;\r\n      flex-direction: column;\r\n      align-items: flex-end;\r\n      gap: 6px;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .space-total-line {\r\n      font-size: 11px;\r\n      color: #666666;\r\n      width: 250px;\r\n      display: flex;\r\n      justify-content: space-between;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .space-total-line span {\r\n      font-weight: 600;\r\n      color: #1A1A1A;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .space-total-line.space-grand {\r\n      font-weight: 600;\r\n      border-top: 1px solid #EAEAEA;\r\n      padding-top: 6px;\r\n      color: #1A1A1A;\r\n      font-size: 12px;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .space-total-line.space-grand span {\r\n      color: #C5A059;\r\n      font-weight: 700;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    /* Proposal Notes */\r\n    .notes-section {\r\n      background: #FAFAFA;\r\n      border-left: 2px solid #C5A059;\r\n      padding: 20px;\r\n      border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0;\r\n      margin-bottom: 45px;\r\n      page-break-inside: avoid;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .notes-section h4 {\r\n      font-size: 10px;\r\n      font-weight: 900;\r\n      text-transform: uppercase;\r\n      letter-spacing: 0.1em;\r\n      color: #1A1A1A;\r\n      margin-bottom: 12px;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .notes-section ol {\r\n      padding-left: 15px;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .notes-section li {\r\n      font-size: 11px;\r\n      color: #555555;\r\n      margin-bottom: 8px;\r\n      line-height: 1.5;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    /* Final Totals block */\r\n    .final-totals-container {\r\n      display: flex;\r\n      justify-content: center;\r\n      page-break-inside: avoid;\r\n      margin-top: 30px;\r\n      margin-bottom: 45px;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .final-totals-card {\r\n      border: 1.5px solid #C5A059;\r\n      background: #FCFAF6;\r\n      width: 100%;\r\n      padding: 30px;\r\n      border-radius: 8px;\r\n      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(197, 160, 89, 0.04);\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .totals-grid-layout {\r\n      display: grid;\r\n      grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;\r\n      gap: 40px;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .totals-details-col {\r\n      border-right: 1px solid #E5DEC9;\r\n      padding-right: 40px;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .totals-grand-col {\r\n      display: flex;\r\n      flex-direction: column;\r\n      justify-content: center;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .final-totals-header {\r\n      font-family: 'Alegreya Sans', sans-serif;\r\n      font-weight: 800;\r\n      font-size: 13px;\r\n      font-weight: 700;\r\n      text-transform: uppercase;\r\n      letter-spacing: 0.1em;\r\n      border-bottom: 1px solid #EAEAEA;\r\n      padding-bottom: 10px;\r\n      margin-bottom: 15px;\r\n      color: #1A1A1A;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .final-line {\r\n      display: flex;\r\n      justify-content: space-between;\r\n      font-size: 12px;\r\n      color: #555555;\r\n      margin-bottom: 8px;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .final-line.discount {\r\n      color: #2E7D32;\r\n      font-weight: 600;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .final-line.grand-total {\r\n      border-top: 2px solid #C5A059;\r\n      padding-top: 12px;\r\n      margin-top: 12px;\r\n      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;\r\n      font-size: 18px;\r\n      font-weight: 700;\r\n      color: #1A1A1A;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .final-line.grand-total span {\r\n      color: #C5A059;\r\n      font-weight: 800;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    /* Closing Page back cover styles */\r\n    .technical-notes-wrapper {\r\n      page-break-before: always;\r\n      page-break-inside: avoid;\r\n      min-height: 720px;\r\n      display: flex;\r\n      flex-direction: column;\r\n      justify-content: center;\r\n      align-items: stretch;\r\n      position: relative;\r\n      padding: 40px 0;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .technical-notes-wrapper::before {\r\n      content: \"\";\r\n      position: absolute;\r\n      top: 0;\r\n      left: 0;\r\n      right: 0;\r\n      height: 2px;\r\n      background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, #C5A059, transparent);\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .technical-notes-wrapper::after {\r\n      content: \"\";\r\n      position: absolute;\r\n      bottom: 0;\r\n      left: 0;\r\n      right: 0;\r\n      height: 2px;\r\n      background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, #C5A059, transparent);\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .technical-notes-section {\r\n      background: #FCFAF6;\r\n      border-left: 3px solid #C5A059;\r\n      border-right: 1px solid #E5DEC9;\r\n      border-top: 1px solid #E5DEC9;\r\n      border-bottom: 1px solid #E5DEC9;\r\n      padding: 25px 30px;\r\n      border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;\r\n      margin: 0;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .technical-notes-section h4 {\r\n      font-family: 'Alegreya Sans', sans-serif;\r\n      font-size: 13px;\r\n      font-weight: 800;\r\n      text-transform: uppercase;\r\n      letter-spacing: 0.1em;\r\n      color: #C5A059;\r\n      margin-bottom: 15px;\r\n      border-bottom: 1px solid #E5DEC9;\r\n      padding-bottom: 8px;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    /* Closing Page back cover styles */\r\n    .closing-page {\r\n      page-break-before: always;\r\n      padding-top: 40px;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .closing-title {\r\n      font-family: 'Alegreya Sans', sans-serif;\r\n      font-size: 22px;\r\n      font-weight: 800;\r\n      letter-spacing: 0.15em;\r\n      text-align: center;\r\n      color: #1A1A1A;\r\n      margin-bottom: 50px;\r\n      border-bottom: 2px solid #C5A059;\r\n      padding-bottom: 20px;\r\n      text-transform: uppercase;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .closing-grid {\r\n      display: block;\r\n      margin-bottom: 50px;\r\n      page-break-inside: avoid;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .policy-block {\r\n      max-width: 700px;\r\n      margin: 0 auto;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .policy-block h4 {\r\n      font-family: 'Alegreya Sans', sans-serif;\r\n      font-size: 14px;\r\n      font-weight: 800;\r\n      text-transform: uppercase;\r\n      letter-spacing: 0.1em;\r\n      color: #C5A059;\r\n      margin-bottom: 20px;\r\n      border-bottom: 1px solid #F1ECE1;\r\n      padding-bottom: 8px;\r\n      text-align: center;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .policy-text {\r\n      font-size: 12px;\r\n      color: #4D4D4D;\r\n      line-height: 1.8;\r\n      text-align: justify;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .policy-text p {\r\n      margin-bottom: 16px;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .notes-list {\r\n      padding-left: 20px;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .notes-list li {\r\n      font-size: 11px;\r\n      color: #4D4D4D;\r\n      margin-bottom: 12px;\r\n      line-height: 1.6;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .financial-terms-grid {\r\n      display: grid;\r\n      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\r\n      gap: 50px;\r\n      border-top: 1px solid #EAEAEA;\r\n      padding-top: 30px;\r\n      margin-bottom: 40px;\r\n      page-break-inside: avoid;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .term-block h5 {\r\n      font-family: 'Alegreya Sans', sans-serif;\r\n      font-size: 12px;\r\n      font-weight: 800;\r\n      text-transform: uppercase;\r\n      letter-spacing: 0.1em;\r\n      color: #C5A059;\r\n      margin-bottom: 15px;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .term-block p {\r\n      font-size: 12px;\r\n      color: #4D4D4D;\r\n      margin-bottom: 8px;\r\n      line-height: 1.6;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .term-block p strong {\r\n      color: #1A1A1A;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .legal-footer {\r\n      text-align: center;\r\n      font-size: 9.5px;\r\n      color: #888888;\r\n      border-top: 1px solid #EAEAEA;\r\n      padding-top: 20px;\r\n      letter-spacing: 0.05em;\r\n      margin-top: 40px;\r\n      font-weight: 600;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    /* Print styles */\r\n    @page {\r\n      size: letter;\r\n      margin: 1.2cm 1.5cm;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    @media print {\r\n      body {\r\n        padding: 0;\r\n        background: transparent;\r\n      }\r\n\r\n      .quote-container {\r\n        border: none;\r\n        box-shadow: none;\r\n        padding: 20px 30px;\r\n        max-width: 100%;\r\n      }\r\n\r\n      .space-section {\r\n        page-break-inside: auto;\r\n        break-inside: auto;\r\n      }\r\n\r\n      tr {\r\n        page-break-inside: avoid;\r\n        break-inside: avoid;\r\n      }\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    /* Cover Spaces List style on Page 1 */\r\n    .cover-spaces-container {\r\n      margin-top: 40px;\r\n      padding-top: 30px;\r\n      border-top: 1px solid #F1ECE1;\r\n      text-align: center;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .cover-spaces-title {\r\n      font-size: 10px;\r\n      font-weight: 900;\r\n      text-transform: uppercase;\r\n      letter-spacing: 0.15em;\r\n      color: #C5A059;\r\n      margin-bottom: 20px;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .cover-spaces-list {\r\n      display: flex;\r\n      justify-content: center;\r\n      flex-wrap: wrap;\r\n      gap: 15px 30px;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .cover-space-item {\r\n      display: flex;\r\n      align-items: center;\r\n      font-size: 13px;\r\n      font-weight: 600;\r\n      color: #4D4D4D;\r\n      letter-spacing: 0.03em;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .cover-space-item .bullet {\r\n      color: #C5A059;\r\n      margin-right: 8px;\r\n      font-size: 11px;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    /* Force Section 2 to start on a new page */\r\n    .detailed-breakdown-section {\r\n      page-break-before: always;\r\n      break-before: page;\r\n      margin-top: 0;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .cover-spaces-layout-wrapper {\r\n      margin-top: 25px;\r\n      display: flex;\r\n      justify-content: center;\r\n      align-items: center;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .cover-spaces-layout-img {\r\n      max-width: 90%;\r\n      max-height: 280px;\r\n      border-radius: 8px;\r\n      border: 1px solid #E5DEC9;\r\n      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03);\r\n    }\r\n  </style>\r\n</head>\r\n\r\n<body>\r\n  <div class=\"quote-container\">\r\n\r\n    <!-- Header -->\r\n    <header class=\"brand-section\">\r\n      <div class=\"brand-logo\">\r\n        <h1>Veta de Oro</h1>\r\n        <p class=\"brand-subtitle\">Estetica y Confort</p>\r\n        <p class=\"brand-contact\">302 5922101 &nbsp;&nbsp;|&nbsp;&nbsp; www.vetadeoro.co &nbsp;&nbsp;|&nbsp;&nbsp; Cra\r\n          72A 71A 57</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"proposal-meta\">\r\n        <h2>PROPUESTA COMERCIAL</h2>\r\n        <p>Nº de Propuesta: {{proposalNumber}}</p>\r\n        <p>Fecha de Emisión: {{proposalDate}}</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </header>\r\n\r\n    <!-- Info Grid -->\r\n    <section class=\"info-grid\">\r\n      {{infoGridHtml}}\r\n    </section>\r\n\r\n    <!-- Executive summary options -->\r\n    <h3 class=\"section-title\">1. Resumen de Cotización</h3>\r\n    <section class=\"options-container\">\r\n      {{optionsHtml}}\r\n    </section>\r\n\r\n    <!-- Centered elegant list of spaces cotizados -->\r\n    <div class=\"cover-spaces-container\">\r\n      <h4 class=\"cover-spaces-title\">Espacios Incluidos</h4>\r\n      <div class=\"cover-spaces-list\">\r\n        {{spacesListHtml}}\r\n      </div>\r\n\r\n    </div>\r\n\r\n    <!-- Spaces breakdown details -->\r\n    <h3 class=\"section-title detailed-breakdown-section\">2. Desglose Detallado de Propuesta ({{activeVariantName}})</h3>\r\n    <section class=\"breakdown-container\">\r\n      {{spacesHtml}}\r\n    </section>\r\n\r\n    <!-- Consideraciones Importantes (Notas Técnicas) debajo del total -->\r\n    <div class=\"technical-notes-wrapper\">\r\n      <section class=\"technical-notes-section\">\r\n        <h4>Consideraciones Importantes</h4>\r\n        <ol class=\"notes-list\">\r\n          <li><strong>Mano de Obra Civil</strong> Esta cotización contempla únicamente los servicios de fabricación e\r\n            instalación de la cocina integral. Si se requiere obra civil, debe realizarse con un profecional\r\n            especializado, veta de oro podra suministrar contactos de confianza, sin embargo el contrato con terceros\r\n            será ageno a la empresa.</li>\r\n          <li><strong>Selección de Acabados:</strong> La textura final y tonos se elegirán sobre muestras físicas que\r\n            presentaremos antes de la producción.</li>\r\n          <li><strong>Vigencia:</strong> Esta propuesta tiene una validez de 15 días hábiles a partir de la fecha de\r\n            emisión.</li>\r\n        </ol>\r\n      </section>\r\n    </div>\r\n\r\n    <!-- Closing Page / Back Page -->\r\n    <section class=\"closing-page\">\r\n\r\n      <div class=\"closing-grid\">\r\n        <div class=\"policy-block\">\r\n          <h4>Políticas Veta de Oro</h4>\r\n          <div class=\"policy-text\">\r\n            <p>En Veta de Oro diseñamos y fabricamos sin intermediarios. Nuestro proceso es directo, preciso y sin\r\n              margen para errores: lo que diseñamos es exactamente lo que usted recibe.</p>\r\n            <p>Más de 25 años de experiencia respaldan nuestra calidad. Contamos con un equipo especializado en\r\n              carpintería, enchapado y acabados, asegurando ejecución impecable en cada detalle.</p>\r\n            <p>Lo que nos distingue no es solo la estética, sino la precisión. Creamos espacios con carácter, hechos\r\n              para durar, reflejando su estilo sin concesiones.</p>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n\r\n      <div class=\"financial-terms-grid\">\r\n        <div class=\"term-block\">\r\n          <h5>Avances y Anticipos</h5>\r\n          <p><strong>50%</strong> producción</p>\r\n          <p><strong>25%</strong> Pre-entrega</p>\r\n          <p><strong>25%</strong> Entrega</p>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div class=\"term-block\">\r\n          <h5>Medios de Pago</h5>\r\n          <p>Bancolombia</p>\r\n          <p>Efectivo</p>\r\n          <p>Tarjeta de crédito <em>(incrementará 2% x cobros de comisión)</em></p>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n\r\n      <div class=\"legal-footer\">\r\n        Veta de Oro es una firma de diseño de Hermanos García Gonzalez SAS | NIT 901421357-9\r\n      </div>\r\n    </section>\r\n\r\n  </div>\r\n</body>\r\n\r\n</html>"
